message.body: Hey Dani, do you have anytime to meet up to play tomorrow or friday?
Hey! It's a wild time. But -- I am free 7-8 tonight....you're a student yah? I'm off work next week and could meet up during the day.
Ive got class tonight until 820, but the weekend or next week ill have time too
I'm away this weekend - next week I'm around during the day Tuesday Wednesday Thursday a bunch
Tuesdays I'm free after 4 and thursdays after 8, my wednesdays are too full
What about later on Tuesday - like at 8:30 or 9?
I forget - are you living in west philly ?
Well I will be downtown already, so uarts is good
Sure, thatll work. We can play at uarts or i could come out to west philly
Cool, whats your email? I'll send you some of my tunes
